{"title":"2020-07-05","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>粘着 vs 粘着。 30 分もわんこするの、すげぇわw</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-194826-intel_NanaoNakajima1.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-194826-intel_NanaoNakajima1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-194717-intel_NanaoNakajima2.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-194717-intel_NanaoNakajima2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>俺なら 5 分で飽きるw</p>\n<hr>\n<p>柴垣のぬこ</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-161059-P_20200705_161059.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-161059-P_20200705_161059.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-161930-P_20200705_161930.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-161930-P_20200705_161930.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>柴垣港も釣り人がきたない… なんで海人(うみんちゅ)はこんなんばっかになるんだろうね？何が違うんだろ？山女はもちろんのこと山男も意外と清潔好きが多い印象だぜ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-162957-P_20200705_162957.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-05/20200705-162957-P_20200705_162957.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>みんぽけ、あんまり登録されないの、ホウオウとかいう余計なの湧いてるからじゃない？雨のせいだけとは思えんが。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>しばらく雨、か。</p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2020-07-06T16:38:40","published":"2020-07-06T16:38:40"}